/*
Note -spiral matrix is 1 indexed in question
The problem can be divided into two parts :- rows=i, columns=j
if(i>=j) => lower triangular matrix including the diagonal
else(i<j) => upper triangular matrix
Each of the above two cases can be subdivded into two more where i is even or i is odd
*/
